narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Washington County Health Department-central is a Clinic/Center, Public Health, State or Local provider based in Hagerstown, MD. From 2018-01 through 2018-05, this provider received $173K in Medicaid payments across 2K claims serving 942 beneficiaries, billing 4 distinct procedure codes.

narrative.title: Key Findings
items: Billing stopped in 2018-05, suggesting this provider is no longer active in Medicaid. Abrupt cessation of billing can be a risk indicator.

narrative.title: Important Context
items: This is a government entity that may serve as a fiscal agent for large populations. Government providers often bill at high volumes due to the scale of public programs they administer.
